content: DONT WASTE YOUR MONEY. OR YOUR TIME! This game is even worse than doodle god. I decided to be less conservative about my hint usage and now I can't use any more hints. There's a time limit. So I played the hero minigame. It says the hero will continue until they need my help. I played the main game for an hour and the hero hadn't done anything. They were still fighting the same enemy as when I left.

Its about the same as the other games. I didn't see a point of the "hero". Im glad i tried it out on playpass. Not all repeated recipes was excluded with the disabler active. Especially when using hints. Wasted hints bad. Some "creations" was poorly thought out. After a while you just stop bothering. I don't know why I was expecting something more.
Good game but the hero needs a faster way of getting xp

Mindless trial and error trying to guess at the developer's moon logic as to what mixes with what to make something random. Few games capture the feeling of being a drudge in a button factory quite as well as this one.

I actually have the exit the game completely to get them to stop. I also don't like that my gold keeps disappearing, it makes it hard to save up for things. I'll rate it 5 stars once fixed.
